# 🚀 CodePilot AI

An AI-powered code intelligence platform that understands GitHub repositories using Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG), semantic search, vector databases, and Gemini.

Instead of simply answering questions, CodePilot AI analyzes an entire codebase, explains architecture, generates documentation, detects technologies, and helps developers understand unfamiliar repositories.

---

# ✨ Features

## Repository Management

- Clone any public GitHub repository
- Parse source code
- Read file contents
- Support multiple programming languages

---

## AI Search

- Semantic code search
- FAISS vector database
- SentenceTransformer embeddings
- Retrieve relevant code snippets
- Repository Question & Answer using Gemini

---

## AI Repository Analysis

### Repository Summary

Generate a high-level overview of the repository.

Includes:

- Project purpose
- Features
- Technologies
- Architecture
- Important folders

---

### File Explanation

Explain any source file.

Includes:

- Purpose
- Classes
- Functions
- Algorithms
- Dependencies
- Time complexity

---

### Folder Explanation

Explain responsibilities of an entire folder.

Example:

```
app/core
```

↓

- Parser
- Chunker
- Embeddings
- Vector Store
- Search

---

### Tech Stack Detection

Automatically detects

- Programming Languages
- Frameworks
- Databases
- Package Managers
- Deployment Tools

---

### Architecture Analysis

AI-generated architecture documentation.

Includes

- High-level overview
- Components
- Workflow
- Data flow
- Mermaid Diagram

---

### API Documentation Generator

Automatically documents backend APIs.

Supports

- FastAPI
- Flask
- Express (basic)

Generates

- HTTP Method
- Route
- Description
- Request Body
- Response
- Status Codes

---

# 🏗 Architecture

```
User
   │
   ▼
FastAPI
   │
Repository Service
   │
──────────────────────────────
│ Clone Repository
│ Parse Repository
│ Chunk Files
│ Generate Embeddings
│ Build FAISS Index
│ Semantic Search
│ Gemini
──────────────────────────────
   │
AI Analysis
```

